                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.77/137.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-01-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 19, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s January 18. It would be advisable in my judgment to have contract
                    examined as suggested, commission to meet immediately and endeavor to report by
                    telegraph within two days in view of end of session of Assembly. See my January
                    18.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
